---
title: Smart Rustic Double Chicken and Feta Meatball Soup with Wild Rice and Garden Veggies
description: Don't sacrifice cozy comforts to be calorie-conscious. This simple, smart recipe delivers on all levels with tender, feta-laced meatballs simmered with aromatic veggies and a wild rice medley!
